{
  "body": "## The problem\r\n\r\nThis [code that shows up in the examples of IO::Socket::INET](https://docs.perl6.org/type/IO::Socket::INET) apparently [crashes when closing the connection](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/50032392/perl6-iosocketinet-could-not-receive-data-from-socket-connection-reset-by-p)\r\n\r\nThis is the error with which it crashes\r\n```\r\nCould not receive data from socket: Connection reset by peer                    \r\n  in block <unit> at server-io-socket.p6 line 9\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Suggestions\r\n\r\nCheck if this is a new bug and file a report where it belongs and/or fix the example code accordingly. \r\n\r\n",
